  "3005490": {
    "name": "Rise Achlys",
    "steam_appid": 3005490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/e5cf5cdcf00f6958e2815cccb6dd9f95.avif?t=1748272729\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras_big/e5cf5cdcf00f6958e2815cccb6dd9f95.avif?t=1748272729 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/a9cb62c7d35880ffdda5cf5393d0b262.poster.avif?t=1748272729\" width=576 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/a9cb62c7d35880ffdda5cf5393d0b262.webm?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>&quot;Rise Achlys&quot;</strong></i>深入探索了一个充满黑暗和戏剧性的叙事，探讨了悲剧、牺牲以及无情的复仇追求等主题。故事的核心是一个名叫阿克利斯的年轻半吸血鬼，他被寄养家庭抚养长大，却目睹了他们惨遭杀害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿克利斯出于复仇的欲望和复活所爱之人的渴望，踏上了艰难的旅程，寻找他真正的父亲，神秘的德古拉。在这危险的道路上，阿克利斯将失去他所珍视的一切，最终成长为一个拥有深厚力量和成熟性格的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/865682b590ba3625a0c3525c1e5a1d5f.poster.avif?t=1748272729\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/865682b590ba3625a0c3525c1e5a1d5f.webm?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/865682b590ba3625a0c3525c1e5a1d5f.mp4?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/05dd525433ca183c4f78debba6eefada.poster.avif?t=1748272729\" width=576 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/05dd525433ca183c4f78debba6eefada.webm?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏上时光之旅的冒险:</strong> 從不同的時代和環境出發，與德古拉的兒子阿克利斯和弗蘭肯斯坦博士一同旅行。穿越過去和未來，開創無盡可能性的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/18d265b8fc73a07c16a8e06db152c5cd.poster.avif?t=1748272729\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/18d265b8fc73a07c16a8e06db152c5cd.webm?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/18d265b8fc73a07c16a8e06db152c5cd.mp4?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精通火焰、暗影与鲜血：</strong>阿克利斯拥有广泛的技能树，涵盖强大的火焰、暗影和血液三大类别的多样能力。您可以选择专攻一种，或者精通全部三种！定制您的能力，打造独特的角色建设。塑造您的吸血鬼个性和游戏风格，成为终极的吸血鬼战士！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/1ec31a41ab800784e97cb6eebe39a953.poster.avif?t=1748272729\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/1ec31a41ab800784e97cb6eebe39a953.webm?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/1ec31a41ab800784e97cb6eebe39a953.mp4?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>变身为三种动物：</strong>作为德古拉之子，阿克利斯拥有变身为狼、老鼠或蝙蝠的能力，这反映了布莱姆·斯托克的原著小说《德古拉》中描述的能力。每种形态都提供独特的技能和优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为蝙蝠，阿克利斯在空中翱翔，优雅地躲避敌人的攻击，直到他的体力消耗殆尽。变成狼形态时，他化身为速度和凶猛的旋风，释放毁灭性的攻击。变成老鼠时，他可以穿过像管道这样的狭窄通道，揭示隐藏在视线之外的秘密路径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/12f1c89ff795c249a981af0217b9612a.poster.avif?t=1748272729\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/12f1c89ff795c249a981af0217b9612a.webm?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/12f1c89ff795c249a981af0217b9612a.mp4?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索非线性关卡：</strong>穿越《崛起的阿克利斯》独特而广阔的宇宙，涉足多样的时期和地点。与复杂的关卡设计互动，包括移动和崩塌的平台以及对您的操作有反应的平台。克服动态障碍，揭示隐藏的路径，与环境中的每一个元素互动。穿越时空，精通每一个精心设计的关卡，打造通往终点的个人路径！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/18c4438d385bee4dac72e66dfec6472e.poster.avif?t=1748272729\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/18c4438d385bee4dac72e66dfec6472e.webm?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005490/extras/18c4438d385bee4dac72e66dfec6472e.mp4?t=1748272729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
